### 3. Data Layer (`/src/data/`)

#### [NEW] [store.js](file:///c:/Users/DELL/Desktop/APPLICATIONS/GroupERP/src/data/store.js)
LocalStorage-based persistence layer with reactive state management.

**Data Models:**
- `categories` — Pole categories (ID, nom, description)
- `produits` — Poles (ID séquentiel, catégorie, désignation, prix_achat, prix_vente, unité)
- `fournisseurs` — Suppliers (ID, raison_sociale, adresse, téléphone, email, RC, NIF, AI, NIS)
- `clients` — Customers (same fields as fournisseurs)
- `settings` — Admin settings (taxes, company info, numbering sequences)
- `devis_achat`, `bc_achat`, `bl_achat`, `facture_achat` — Purchase documents
- `devis_vente`, `bc_vente`, `bl_vente`, `facture_vente` — Sales documents
- `stock_mouvements` — Stock movements
- `reglements` — Payments

